text: So I asked Alexa to play me some Hendrix music. First she played Hey Joe which I'd been bingeing on. Then came his opening at Woodstock. And then All Along the Watchtower. Which was really emotional for me. It's already been a heavy duty emotional day. Why not go deeper! After that he asks Are You Experienced? Hey for such a young man, he died at 27, he was very self-aware and surroundings-aware.
